                <fr:p>In the ring of gaussian integers we introduce the function <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[N: a+ib \in  \mathbb  Z[i] \mapsto  a^2+b^2]]></fr:tex> which we call norm function.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
